"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"【細味經典Something Timeless】<br />\n戲迷最期待嘅畫面出現了❗️一直備受影迷推崇嘅兩部偉大鉅作😍《月黑高飛》同《瘟室》(The Room)🤣預售喇🎟！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n🥇高踞IMDb史上最佳電影第一位！<br />\n上映25年來觸動無數戲迷🥺<br />\n《月黑高飛》25周年經典重映&hearts;️👉🏻<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zby73A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zby73A&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=abdaae8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zby73A</a><br />\n日期：6月21日｜7月12日<br />\n時間：5:30PM｜7:50PM<br />\n地點：海運戲院<br />\n<br />\n🤡被喻為爛片界嘅聖經<br />\n百年難得一遇嘅教材級神片✨<br />\n《瘟室》重口味重映🏈👉🏻<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MEbEzh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MEbEzh&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=b52e5115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MEbEzh</a><br />\n日期：7月3日｜7月4日<br />\n時間：8:30PM｜8:30PM<br />\n地點：海運戲院<br />\n🥄為咗保障戲院衞生，今次要請大家收返埋啲私伙匙羹🤣<br />\n我哋會特別為每位Fan屎準備定一set廿隻匙羹（票價已包含匙羹費用），等大家可以坦盪盪咁入場，然後狠狠地毫無保留地瘋狂掟羹🥳🥳🥳🥳<br />\n<br />\n📣至於好多影迷期待嘅《發條橙》，預售日期好快會公佈，敬請期待🤗<br />\n#不能錯過的好戲 <br />\n#月黑高飛 #AShawshankRedemption #TheRoom #瘟室 <br />\n#細味經典 #SomethingTimeless #海運戲院 #ghcinemas"},{"pid":"ea8d53bb14d7bdedaf83465440924175cfc65015","tid":2040341,"uid":12594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d94b0aaf0d85ea5363c5d8a9d770b6e016baf1","tid":2040341,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee3e8d71ccdc4e9e9c9c2250c20d8ff75c970cb","tid":2040341,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"【以你的片名字呼喚我】<br />\n<br />\n心水清的fans，有冇留意其實我哋一直都用返The Room來稱呼The Room，而甚少試用「瘟室」？當初想到要作個中文名，其實我哋是拒絕的，一來是懶，二是來擔心失去神髓，三來是擔心沒有00民峰等大師指點會運濟，四來是真係懶。<br />\n<br />\n到公映場時，戲院方面話點都要有個中文名印戲飛（甚麼鬼原因？），建議了一些片名，我哋覺得不太適合，於是用了5分鐘時間，鳩度了幾個名，又用了10分鐘時間，吹了幾段賣橋的文字。最後《瘟室》中標，仲獲得才子方俊傑讚賞為「一個不落俗套的中文名字」，沾沾了好久！（有字有真相：<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180125/57745015）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57745015%EF%BC%89&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=7cc44915\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57745015%EF%BC%89&h=40daeebb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180125/57745015）</a><br />\n<br />\n最近睇返呢堆名同背後原因，真係有夠戇鳩，想同大家分享，仲打算整個投票睇下大家喜歡邊個名，點知Facebook投票唔俾我哋有多過2個options，所以大家都俾Facebook DQ咗，連投票嘅資格都冇呀！<br />\n<br />\n想膠流就留個言話我哋知你的喜好啦，賜教賜教！<br />\n<br />\n有興趣再次細味經典嘅朋友，有得買飛啦🏈👉🏻<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MEbEzh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MEbEzh&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=b52e5115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MEbEzh</a><br />\n日期：7月3日｜7月4日<br />\n時間：8:30PM｜8:30PM<br />\n地點：海運戲院<br />\n<br />\n#瘟室 #爛國民 #戙房 #無掩雞籠<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/296993197486086/posts/919311848587548/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F296993197486086%2Fposts%2F919311848587548%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=000bb39b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/296993197486086/posts/919311848587548/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"009107bac8cb1e3ca3a9e90e595c08c27bb3ff20","tid":2040341,"uid":4260,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac